{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4fe74ae37c","title":"对地方党委领导新闻事业的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7cd81f9e0d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"4fe74ae37c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958.1-1960）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76e2cfedc4","type":"paragraph","text":"对大跃进报导的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"0ab66291e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年末于武昌）","index":1,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"dd5b21a425","type":"paragraph","text":"要实事求是，不要浮夸，要作冷静的促进派，要鼓实劲，不要鼓虚劲，冲天的干劲要与严格的科学的态度相结合。","index":2,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"3d296debc5","type":"paragraph","text":"对地方党委导新间事业的指示","index":3,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"a9a42fe06b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年）","index":4,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"c1861349eb","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年，新华社国内分社和人民日报记者站合并，体制下放给地方党委，会向主席汇报此事，主席说。","index":5,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"a6cc04b6b0","type":"paragraph","text":"早就应该这样做，过去（分社）省也管不了，现在这个办法是适应国家的情况的。省委管比你们有办法，分社也就不孤单了，就有依靠了。","index":6,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"7efa6f1950","type":"paragraph","text":"关于造船方斜的指示","index":7,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"f8761c1cad","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年月）","index":8,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"d3d84c9d4f","type":"paragraph","text":"在我国现代工业、现代农业、现代科学文化发展的基础上，国防力量的建设不仅要作好积极防御的准备工作，同时还要准备一且帝国主义向我国发动侵略战争时，在打败敌人之后，实施战略反攻和战略追击，把侵略者赶同他们的本土，坚决、干净、彻底全部消灭之，解放那里的人民，以便侵略战争永远不再发生。为此，除了继续加强陆军和室军建设以外，必须大搞造船工业，建立海上铁路，以便在今后若干年内建设一支强大的海上战斗力量。","index":9,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"}],"page":{"id":"255572b89f","publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"4fe74ae37c","start":199,"end":199}},"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"3aa17b0df3","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1958年，新华社国内分社和人民日报记者站合并。这是毛泽东在听取关于此事汇报时，对地方党委领导新闻事业的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0fe3ef45a5","type":"title","text":"对地方党委领导新闻事业的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"3aa17b0df3","type":"paragraph","text":"早就应该这样做，过去（分社）省也管不了，现在这个办法是适应国家的情况的。省委管比你们有办法，分社也就不孤单了，就有依靠了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"}],"page":{"id":"b9e203982f","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c","start":156,"end":156}}}},"__N_SSG":true}